NavInspector   = Alt + D1
NavSearch      = Alt + D2
NavDetections  = Alt + D3
NavProperties  = Alt + D4

CopyHex        = Control + C
CopyCArray     = Control + Shift + C
CopyPlainText  = Control + Alt + C

Undo           = Control + Z
FullUndo       = Control + Shift + Z

OpenDisassembler = Control + D
OpenDecompiler   = Control + E

RunScript      = F5
ViewBytes      = F3
ViewYaraMatches = Shift + F3
